      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation are documented and sufficiently representative of the intended CPB operating environment.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal blood pump experiments were conducted at flow rates of 2–6 L/min and rotational speeds of 2000–3500 RPM using bovine blood with documented hematocrit and temperature. These conditions bracket the 5 flow-speed combinations evaluated in the COU."
