      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index values agree with experimental measurements within accepted tolerance bands at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH values compared against experimental hemolysis data show mean absolute error of 8.3% across all 5 operating points. Agreement is within the MRL 2 tolerance band and supports use of the model for worst-case identification."
