    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements for Model Risk Level 2. CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index values demonstrate sufficient agreement with FDA experimental data to support identification of worst-case operating conditions. The model is accepted for use in the regulatory submission supporting tolerance analysis for the Class II CPB device.",
